# <type>(<scope>): <subject>
#
# <body>
#
# Sprint: Week X (YYYY-MM-DD to YYYY-MM-DD)
# Todo: todo-123, todo-456
# Fixes: blocker-789 (if fixing a sprint blocker)
# Co-authored-by: Name <email@example.com>
#
# Type must be one of the following:
# * feat:      ✨ New feature
# * fix:       🐛 Bug fix
# * docs:      📚 Documentation only changes
# * style:     💄 Formatting, missing semicolons, etc; no code change
# * refactor:  ♻️ Refactoring production code
# * perf:      ⚡ Performance improvements
# * test:      🧪 Adding tests, refactoring test; no production code change
# * build:     🔧 Changes affecting build system or external dependencies
# * ci:        👷 Changes to CI configuration files and scripts
# * chore:     🔨 Updating build tasks, package manager configs, etc
# * revert:    ⏪ Reverting a previous commit
# * sprint:    🎯 Sprint-related changes (planning, documentation)
# * todo:      ✅ Todo item completion or updates
# * blocker:   🚨 Fixes sprint blockers
# * automation:🤖 Automation and tooling improvements
#
# Scope (optional): app name (web|talentexcel|sevapremi|10xgrowth|admin) or component
#
# Subject line:
# * Use imperative, present tense: "change" not "changed" nor "changes"
# * Don't capitalize first letter
# * No dot (.) at the end
# * Maximum 50 characters
#
# Body (optional):
# * Wrap at 72 characters
# * Use imperative mood
# * Include motivation for the change and contrasts with previous behavior
# * Always include Sprint and Todo information for feature work
#
# Footer (optional):
# * Reference issues: "Closes #123", "Fixes #456"
# * Include breaking changes: "BREAKING CHANGE: description"
# * Sprint integration: "Sprint: Week X", "Todo: todo-123"
#
# Examples:
# feat(web): add user profile dashboard
# 
# Add comprehensive user profile with edit capabilities,
# avatar upload, and preferences management.
# 
# Sprint: Week 2 (2025-07-08 to 2025-07-14)
# Todo: todo-123, todo-124
# Closes #45
#
# fix(auth): resolve session timeout issue
#
# Users were being logged out unexpectedly due to
# incorrect token refresh logic.
#
# Sprint: Week 2 (2025-07-08 to 2025-07-14)
# Todo: todo-125
# Fixes: blocker-12
# Closes #78